works.description: For people stuck to a green agenda, pedal power seems to be a suitable alternative. While we were still in the process of appreciating the limited edition Digitizer track bike worth $5000 or Damien Hirst’s bike for $500,000, Germany-based Vandeyk Contemporary Cycles with its hand crafted designs silently made its mark. The artistic version has been brought to life by designer Harry Seifert based in Germany.
